gText_Truck_Intro::
	.string "{COLOR DARK_GRAY}The moving truck rumbles along the\n"
	.string "winding road to LITTLEROOT TOWN…{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "You sit quietly among the boxes,\n"
	.string "watching the HOENN countryside\l"
	.string "roll by through the small window.\p"
	.string "The DRIVER glances back through\n"
	.string "the rear window.\p"
	.string "DRIVER: Pretty quiet back there, kid.\n"
	.string "Nervous about the move?\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: A little, I guess.\n"
	.string "It's been a while since we've\l"
	.string "moved somewhere new.{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: HOENN's a good place for\n"
	.string "fresh starts. I've been driving\l"
	.string "this route for years.\p"
	.string "Starting over can be a good thing\n"
	.string "sometimes, you know?\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: Starting over, huh?\n"
	.string "If only it was that easy…{COLOR WHITE}$"

gText_Truck_MysteriousBox::
	.string "An old wooden box with strange\n"
	.string "symbols carved into its surface.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: What's with this box?\n"
	.string "These symbols look ancient.{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: Oh, that old thing? Found it\n"
	.string "in storage. Previous owner left it.\l"
	.string "Figured someone might want it.\p"
	.string "The box feels warm to the touch,\n"
	.string "despite the cool air in the truck.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: It's… glowing slightly.\n"
	.string "That's not normal, is it?{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: HOENN's full of strange\n"
	.string "things, kid. You'll get used to it.$"

gText_Truck_DevenCorpBox::
	.string "A sleek metallic container bearing\n"
	.string "the DEVON CORPORATION logo.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: DEVON CORPORATION?\n"
	.string "What kind of company is that?{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: Big tech company in RUSTBORO.\n"
	.string "They make all sorts of gadgets\l"
	.string "for trainers.\p"
	.string "Oh, that reminds me! There's\n"
	.string "something in there I found after\l"
	.string "my last delivery from them.\p"
	.string "Inside, you spot a peculiar bracelet\n"
	.string "with a crystalline centerpiece.\p"
	.string "DRIVER: They said I could keep it if I\n"
	.string "wanted, but jewelry's not really\l"
	.string "my style.\p"
	.string "You can have it if you like, kid.\n"
	.string "Looks like it'd suit a young\l"
	.string "trainer better than an old driver.\p"
	.string "{PLAYER} obtained the MEGA RING!\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: This bracelet feels…\n"
	.string "familiar somehow. Like it's been\l"
	.string "waiting for me.{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: Huh, that's interesting.\n"
	.string "Maybe it was meant to be yours.$"

gText_Truck_MemoryBox::
	.string "A simple cardboard box labeled\n"
	.string "'MEMORIES' in your mother's\l"
	.string "handwriting.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: Mom packed our old photos\n"
	.string "and stuff in here.{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: Memories are important.\n"
	.string "But don't let them hold you back\l"
	.string "from making new ones.\p"
	.string "HOENN's got plenty of adventures\n"
	.string "waiting for someone like you.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: Someone like me?{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: Trust me, kid. The POKéMON\n"
	.string "here can sense things about people\l"
	.string "that even we don't know about\l"
	.string "ourselves.$"

gText_Truck_PlayerReflection::
	.string "DRIVER: Whatever you're leaving\n"
	.string "behind, HOENN has a way of helping\l"
	.string "people find their true path.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: You really think so?{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: I've seen it happen before.\n"
	.string "Young trainers come here carrying\l"
	.string "all sorts of burdens…\p"
	.string "But there's something special about\n"
	.string "this region. The legends say the\l"
	.string "land itself chooses its champions.\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: Champions, huh…{COLOR WHITE}$"

gText_Truck_ReadyToExit::
	.string "The truck begins to slow down.\p"
	.string "DRIVER: Here we are! LITTLEROOT TOWN!\n"
	.string "Time to start that new chapter\l"
	.string "of yours!\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: Thanks for the ride…\n"
	.string "and the advice. And the bracelet.{COLOR WHITE}\p"
	.string "DRIVER: Don't mention it, kid.\n"
	.string "Something tells me you're going\l"
	.string "to need it.\p"
	.string "MOM: {PLAYER}! Come on out and see\n"
	.string "our new home!\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}PLAYER: Here goes nothing…{COLOR WHITE}$"
